<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1902-09-10T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1902-09-10T00:00:00-05:00" n="816" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d816">
                        <head><hi rend="italic">President <persName type="from">Regalado</persName>
                                to President <persName type="to">Roosevelt</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Translation.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">San
                                        Salvador</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1902-09-10"><hi rend="italic">September 10,
                                    1902</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>I express to Your Excellency the painful sentiments caused me by the
                            occurrence that befell you, and I beg you to accept the expression of my
                            sympathy for that unfortunate event.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Tomas Regalado.</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>